---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Automation for the Baking Industry — Formic"
  description="Labor shortages, overtime, downtime, missed deliveries. Baking manufacturing is tough — Formic makes it easier. ABA-partnered robotic palletizing and case packing under Full Service Automation."
  ogTitle="Automation for Commercial Baking Manufacturers — Formic"
  ogDescription="Fully managed robotic palletizing and case packing for commercial bakers. No CapEx, deployed in weeks. American Bakers Association partner."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/results/commercial-baking" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .ind-yt-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#000;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .ind-yt-wrap iframe{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0}
    .ind-qbox{background:var(--white);padding:34px 32px;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);margin:18px 0 22px}
    .ind-qbox blockquote{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:19px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.5;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-.005em}
    .ind-qbox .ind-qattr{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/results">Results</a><span class="sep">/</span>Commercial Baking
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Industry · Commercial Baking</div>
    <h1>Automation for <br><em>the baking industry</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Labor shortages. Overtime costs. Excess downtime. Missed deliveries. Baking manufacturing is tough. We make it easier.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/stories/uncle-crumbles/1749483799-screenshot-2025-06-09-at-8-43-04-am.png">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · commercial baking</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">$0 CapEx · Deployed in weeks</div>
      <h2>Automate your line. <em>Deploy in weeks</em>.</h2>
      <p>Palletizing and case packing that work from day one. No hiring. No retraining. No headaches. Just consistent output.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Say yes to more orders — capacity that turns into revenue</li>
        <li>Modernize legacy and family-bakery operations without a CapEx project</li>
        <li>Fully supported by Formic engineers, 24/7</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="larr">Talk to a baking automation engineer →</a>
      <a class="dl-btn" href="/downloads/Formic-Best-Practices-Baking-Uncle-Crumbles.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="dl-btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
        <span class="dl-btn-text">
          <span class="dl-btn-title">Commercial baking best practices guide</span>
          <span class="dl-btn-meta">PDF · 6.3 MB</span>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/mi-rancho/1717609049-formic-mi-rancho-photos-4-of-17.jpg" alt="Formic palletizing on a Mi Rancho tortilla line — bakery industry automation" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Bakery palletizing · 24/7</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/uncle-crumbles/1749483799-screenshot-2025-06-09-at-8-43-04-am.png" alt="Uncle Crumbles bakery floor — next-chapter automation" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Uncle Crumbles · the next chapter</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Customer story</div>
      <h2>How automation is powering the next chapter <em>at Uncle Crumbles</em>.</h2>
      <div class="ind-qbox">
        <blockquote>"The equipment we're bringing in can handle more intricate cartoning and bulk items our customers want. The more we can say yes, the more opportunities we win. Historically, though, the mindset was just to work with what we had, and what we had wasn't working."</blockquote>
        <div class="ind-qattr">James Shutts · CEO, Uncle Crumbles</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/stories/uncle-crumbles" class="larr">Read the Uncle Crumbles story →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px">
    <div class="db-tag">Partnership</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 16px">Committed to making automation <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">accessible for bakers</em>.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(240,245,241,.72);max-width:720px;margin:0">We've partnered with the American Bakers Association to help its 350+ members enhance production capabilities by making automation simple and accessible.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Automation so simple, it's a piece of cake</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 28px">Automate your bakery lines — <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">for $0 in CapEx</em>.</h2>
    <div class="ind-yt-wrap">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SD0UMnNYR1E" title="Formic Full Service Automation" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Get started with automation<br><em>today</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/results" class="btn-ctawh">All Industries</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
